        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 54. Labels. i Bulimus schmidti Pfeiffer, 1854 ii Bulimus scitulus Reeve, 1849 iii Otostomus scitus H. Adams, 1867 iv Bulimulus (Drymaeus) selli Preston, 1909 v Bulimus serotinus Morelet, 1860 vi Bulimus serratus Pfeiffer, 1855." , "Figure 44. Drymaeus species. A-C Drymaeus (Drymaeus) cylindricus da Costa, 1901, lectotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.42 (H = 30.6) D-F Drymaeus (Drymaeus) scitulus (Reeve, 1849), lectotype NHMUK 1975217 (H = 29.5) G-I Drymaeus (Drymaeus) vespertinus (Pfeiffer, 1858), lectotype NHMUK 1975471 (H = 34.6) J-L Drymaeus (Drymaeus) pseudofusoides da Costa, 1906, holotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.11 (H = 33.6) M-O Drymaeus (Drymaeus) lophoicus (d'Orbigny, 1835), paralectotype NHMUK 1854.12.4.135 (H = 32.7). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26821" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26713" .

